{"tid":1295534,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[麥記]我真係好撚嬲","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:21:29.000Z","uid":108519,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec135d44dd956591b3d22a08fb5aedb1a5cb57e","tid":1295534,"uid":108519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"屌,真係扯撚晒火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n幾廿年前人地叫我去佢屋企玩<br />\r\n仲話有靚女推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n諗住買十八件雞餐去人地屋食<br />\r\n實夠晒霸氣<br />\r\n等班女求我叫我比一件佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n咁咪去附近間麥記叫十八件雞餐拎走<br />\r\n可能我之前成日去叫乾炒牛河<br />\r\n店員都放晒我入黑名單<br />\r\n我一入店已經響晒警鐘<br />\r\n咁我就走去櫃台好霸氣咁叫18件雞拎走<br />\r\n店員見我終於唔叫乾炒牛河就係咁多謝我<br />\r\n我心諗乾炒牛河好失禮咩,你地班友真不懂享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n跟住我一臉威風咁去到人地屋<br />\r\n見到mk仔係到請緊班女食壽司<br />\r\n仲要唔係明將又冇紅豆軍艦<br />\r\n我心諗:竟然明將都唔撚食,食呢d咁既壽司<br />\r\n於是我手執十條薯條,將全部女手中既<br />\r\n三文魚,蟹子,吞拿魚壽司全部一一打走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n然後從身後掏出一盒<br />\r\n十八件麥樂雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n班女見到我咁型已經2眼發光<br />\r\n我一打開盒雞,佢地一手搶一件,已經一手執一件雞等點醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n佢地眼神閃閃,流晒西水咁等我拎4款醬出黎<br />\r\n當然我都要成全佢地啦<br />\r\n我一打開外賣袋,冇醬既!?<br />\r\n肯定收埋左係外賣紙袋到啦<br />\r\n我一手撕開紙袋,都係冇醬喎<br />\r\n我即刻叫晒成班保鑣過黎進行地毯式搜索<br />\r\n都係冇,冇可能,呢單肯定係唔一般既案件<br />\r\n我即刻請晒金田一,柯南過黎<br />\r\n就連讀心神探都黎埋<br />\r\n點解都搵唔到既?<br />\r\n班女已經你眼望我眼<br />\r\n睇住我既霸氣指數直插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n我要出絕招啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n我即刻手執可樂既飲管<br />\r\n大叫:速速前,麥樂雞醬!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n點撚知都係唔work<br />\r\n於是我就最後衝刺<br />\r\n我問埋燦神都係依然冇法搵到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n身後既人無一不在恥笑我<br />\r\n於是我帶淚跑番屋企<br />\r\n過左幾廿年,眼見當年既mk妹已經比人屌到變牛肺<br />\r\n我好後悔...好後悔<br />\r\n點解當時搵唔到果4盒醬<br />\r\n搞到今時今日咁<br />\r\n我走到街上散下心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n我聽住歌,睇到前面有一熟悉既身影,原來係當年serve我既店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n我地兩眼交流左幾分鐘<br />\r\n心中有說不出的千言萬語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n店員說:我唔記得比醬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n屌,火都黎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815e936a9f1b460582ccadc948b5a92b0d048a88","tid":1295534,"uid":6366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07449b196968783039f84553557a9eeea67f0fcd","tid":1295534,"uid":246853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"TLNR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8397d3af054169e9e135f5a7d1ecd6eec9790c0","tid":1295534,"uid":34138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5370aa38c0653c6a8808443e76ccd0f16ad6f42","tid":1295534,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}